You can find information on genera and species in the following packages.

()		lang/hermit.ast
Boolean		lang/boolean.ast
Char		lang/char.ast
Comparison	lang/compare.ast
ExceptionSpecies lang/except.ast
FileMode	system/io.ast
Integer		math/stdnum.ast
Natural		math/stdnum.ast
Rational	math/stdnum.ast
Real		math/stdnum.ast
UnknownKey      logic/unknown.ast

ANY		lang/misc.ast
ENUMERATED	lang/rank.ast
EQ		lang/compare.ast
INTEGER		math/stdnum.ast
ORDER		lang/compare.ast
RANKED		lang/rank.ast
RATIONAL	math/stdnum.ast
RATRING		math/stdnum.ast
RFIELD		math/stdnum.ast
RRING		math/stdnum.ast
REAL		math/stdnum.ast

